---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Buzz Co Curbing | Our Story & Philosophy"
  description="Founded in 2010 in Cache Valley, Buzz Co Curbing started with one truck and a passion for clean concrete work. Now serving Utah with same-week scheduling and 4.9-star reviews."
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-32 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <p class="font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-warm-muted mb-4">OUR STORY</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-section-heading font-bold text-dark mb-12">About Buzz Co Curbing</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Buzz Co Curbing started in 2010 with one truck, a concrete machine, and a simple belief: homeowners deserve curbing that looks great and gets installed without the runaround. Founder Justin Anderson launched the company in Cache Valley, Utah, with no marketing budget — just a commitment to show up, quote honestly, and do the job right.
        </p>

        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          That first year, Justin handled every job himself. He'd show up so both spouses could be home, walk the yard together, sketch the layout, and give a firm price on the spot. No "we'll email you a quote in three days." No pressure. If you said yes, the crew was scheduled that same week. That rhythm — on-site quote, fast turnaround — became the backbone of how Buzz Co operates to this day.
        </p>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8 md:p-12 my-12">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-6">We design it with you, on your property, before we pour.</h2>
          <p class="font-body text-dark/80 leading-relaxed">
            We walk every job before it starts. No surprises, no cookie-cutter layouts. Your curbing should look like it was designed for your yard. Because it was.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-dark mt-16 mb-6">The Franchise Story</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Buzz Co grew organically through word of mouth. Cache Valley homeowners told their friends. Friends told neighbors. The reputation spread: fair pricing, clean work, and a crew that actually showed up when they said they would. By 2020, demand had stretched beyond Cache Valley. Rather than turn people away or overextend, Justin built a franchise model — bringing on operators who shared the same standards and the same commitment to personal service.
        </p>

        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Today Buzz Co operates across three territories: Cache Valley (Logan and surrounding cities), the Northern Wasatch Front (Ogden through Salt Lake City), and Utah Valley (Sandy through Provo). Each territory has its own operator, its own crew, and its own phone number — but the same process, the same quality, and the same promise: on-site quote, same-week install.
        </p>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8 md:p-12 my-12">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-6">What Makes Us Different</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 font-body text-dark/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="font-data text-accent font-bold shrink-0">01</span>
              <span><strong class="text-dark">On-site walkthroughs.</strong> We schedule when both homeowners can be there. No guessing, no second call — we design and quote together.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="font-data text-accent font-bold shrink-0">02</span>
              <span><strong class="text-dark">Same-week installation.</strong> Most jobs are scheduled and poured within days of your quote. No weeks of waiting.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="font-data text-accent font-bold shrink-0">03</span>
              <span><strong class="text-dark">14 colors, 10 stamp patterns.</strong> Full customization without the premium price. We match your home, your stone, your landscape.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="font-data text-accent font-bold shrink-0">04</span>
              <span><strong class="text-dark">Still hands-on.</strong> Justin walks every Logan job before it starts. The founder is still in the field, still checking quality, still answering the phone.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class="font-body text-lg text-dark/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our customers have left us a 4.9-star rating on Google. Those reviews aren't from paid promotions — they're from homeowners who got a fair quote, a fast install, and curbing they're proud to show off. That's the standard we've built over 14 years, and it's the standard we'll keep.
        </p>

        <!-- Real project photo showcase -->
        <div class="mt-16 mb-4">
          <p class="font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-warm-muted mb-6">REAL PROJECTS</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            <img
              src="/images/gallery/stone-home-decorative-curbing-mulch-bed-utah.jpg"
              alt="Decorative concrete curbing bordering mulch beds at a stone exterior home in Utah"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/gallery/winding-concrete-curbing-lawn-border-utah.jpg"
              alt="Winding S-curve concrete curbing separating lawn from mulch beds with Utah lake views"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/gallery/paver-patio-curbing-backyard-aerial-utah.jpg"
              alt="Aerial view of cobblestone paver patio with concrete curbing in a Utah backyard"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-dark/40 mt-3 text-center">
            A sample of completed projects across Utah. <a href="/gallery/" class="text-accent hover:underline">See the full gallery →</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
          <p class="font-body text-dark/60 mb-4">Ready to see what Buzz Co can do for your yard?</p>
          <a href="/logan/get-estimate/" class="btn-primary">
            <span class="btn-bg" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="btn-text">Get a Free Estimate</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
